Package: starship-os
Version: 2.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-venv, curl
Recommends: ollama, nats-server
Suggests: nvidia-cuda-toolkit | rocm-dev
Maintainer: Starship OS <ops@starship.os>
Homepage: https://github.com/andromi-hash/starship-os
 Description: Starship OS
  AI agent-first OS layer for Ubuntu 24.04. Agents on NATS/JetStream with
  local Ollama inference. Includes starshipctl, StarAgent, Proxy/Romi/Ergo,
  C2 dashboard :8788, fleet manager, C11 sandbox/policyexec, multi-tenant NATS.
  Install roots: /opt/starship, /etc/starship.
